1. Default Connection
**********************************************
* Board_Connector * Pin Name * RPi_Connector *
*       1         *     GND  *      GND      *
*       2         *     MOSI *      GPIO_10  *
*       3         *     SCK  *      GPIO_11  *
*       4         *     CS   *      GPIO_22  *
*       5         *     MISO *      GPIO_9   *
*       6         *    +3.3V *      +3.3V    *
**********************************************

2. Config.txt Description.
'spi': - NEVER CHANGE
'bus': - SPI Bus Number
'device': - SPI Device Number
'max_speed_hz': - SPI Bus Frequency (Hz)
'spi_mode': - SPI Bus Mode
'cs_pin': Number of CS pin (GPIO)
'modules': - Number of connected PCB modules
'images': - Number of images in base
'floor':  - Number of floor images in base
'wall':  - Number of wall images in base
'room':  - Number of rooms
'timeout':  - Timeout to reset the image default

